{"tid":494072,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"小行星掠過地球 隔天才發現！","createTime":"2017-12-09T08:27:39.000Z","updateTime":"2017-12-09T15:21:26.000Z","uid":10788,"like":1,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"307752483d56bbcaa79a290df7d54e4852f1900b","tid":494072,"uid":10788,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-09T08:27:39.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://news.ltn.com.tw\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw&d=0f1PjH4DZh8cit4d2DdfqE%2FDJpISyAq9ELy6OyFxwDc%3D&h=4ece8f2b\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw&h=8e5bc35b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">news.ltn.com.tw</a><br />\n捏把冷汗！鯨魚大般小行星掠過地球 NASA隔天才發現 - 國際 - 自由時報電子報<br />\n根據「電腦網路內容分級處理辦法」修正條文第六條第三款規定，已於網站首頁或各該限制級網頁，依台灣網站分級推廣基金會規定作標示。 台灣網站分級推廣基金會（TICRF）網站：<a href=\"http://www.ticrf.org.tw\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.ticrf.org.tw&d=0f1PjH4DZh8cit4d2DdfqE%2FDJpISyAq9ELy6OyFxwDc%3D&h=26d2aa8d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www.ticrf.org.tw</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n一顆直徑16公尺至32公尺如鯨魚般大小的小行星，上月9日與地球擦身而過，NASA隔天才發現有這顆小行星路過。示意圖，非「2017 VL2」。（美聯社）<br />\n<br />\n2017-12-09 15:01<br />\n〔即時新聞／綜合報導〕一顆直徑16公尺至32公尺如鯨魚般大小的小行星，上月9日與地球擦身而過，美國太空總署（NASA）後知後覺，隔天才發現有這顆小行星路過，如果該小行星撞擊地表，可以將方圓6公里以內的所有生物給摧毀。<br />\n<br />\n綜合外媒報導，一顆名為「2017 VL2」，直徑約16至32公尺的小行星於11月9日，以每秒9公里的速度，距地球約11.7萬公里的距離掠過，此距離僅為地球與月球的三分之一；11月10日，夏威夷的冒納羅亞天文台（Mauna Loa Observatory）觀測「2017 VL2」，通報NASA，但是科學家計算其軌跡後，驚訝地發現「2017 VL2」昨天險些撞上地球，令人捏把冷汗。<br />\n<br />\n如果現「2017 VL2」撞擊地球，可以造成如摧毀整個紐約市大小地表的災難；NASA針對所有可能造成災難，直徑在1公里以上的近地天體 （near-Earth object，NEO）都要造冊監看，而「2017 VL2」掠過地球，顯示小行星監測仍不能完全鎖定所有近地天體，據計算，「2017 VL2」要到2125年才會再次接近地球。<br />\n<br />\n下週六（16日）還有一顆直徑達5公里的小行星「3200 Phaethon」會掠過地球，雙子座流星雨的流星體就是來自於它，是唯一已被確認與小行星有關的流星雨。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n新聞送上來！快加入自由電子報APP、LINE好友<br />\n<br />\n<br />\ndiv &gt; ul &gt; li&quot;data-target-index=&quot;9&quot;data-target-pos=&quot;AFTER&quot;&gt;<br />\n切換到豐富的查看<br />\n房屋大的小行星擦過地球一天後才被發現 &mdash; 大紀元 (新聞發布)<br />\n驚險！小行星差點撞地球NASA竟隔天才察覺 &mdash; 台灣蘋果日報 體育"},{"pid":"ce97d266892b0a23411336b64702f70b0139a5a5","tid":494072,"uid":10788,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-09T08:28:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e31b3fed67ad746b5fa4be82a6ae6e704d32e294","tid":494072,"uid":131686,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-09T08:29:25.000Z","msg":"天滅<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f4ebffa56f1bbb72cd01fc092f7ff1a5b5826511","tid":494072,"uid":92459,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-09T08:31:09.000Z","msg":"早幾日發現又點, 炸爆佢?"},{"pid":"9924fd35c6f714970138605e122f6517017f5bee","tid":494072,"uid":104443,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-09T08:40:42.000Z","msg":"消滅方圓六公里所有生物<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n點解唔跌落中南海<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fa65cd51eb904eba90a90e6ba0f59a6c1f575da4","tid":494072,"uid":27396,"like":0,"dislike":5,"score":-5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-09T08:49:53.000Z","msg":"是但啦 撞還撞 唔好搞到我返工遲到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"93ffce466bd6049fa68129c3f127916eefbaf9fe","tid":494072,"uid":5253,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-09T08:52:35.000Z","msg":"Nasa一早知喇 不過緊係完左先講 廢事制造恐仿"},{"pid":"6672bd8db63125e02e9be028bcb926bcb04ca5e4","tid":494072,"uid":20522,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-09T08:53:01.000Z","msg":"wow"},{"pid":"81b1a21445e736a34163904a1660fe49d65bfb4e","tid":494072,"uid":62599,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-09T08:53:27.000Z","msg":"絕世天劫"},{"pid":"50924273c8f6ebeacf54cb2cf15ca8cd540e55c9","tid":494072,"uid":75326,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-09T09:56: